ns for how feedback processes affect the distribution and\nkinematics of gas and the environment around galaxies out to scales of several\nMegaparsecs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jul 2022 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
