d horizontal branch sample, we find a mass\ndistribution consistent with a single value. We emphasise the importance of\nseismic studies of GCs since they could potentially resolve major uncertainties\nin stellar theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jul 2022 02:31:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
